FCWM3027AS.Name: 30" Electric Wall Oven and Microwave Combination
FCWM3027AS.Description: The Frigidaire 30" Microwave Combination Oven with Fan Convection allows you to achieve faster, more even multi-rack baking results, all in an extra large, 5.3 cu.ft. oven cavity!   It also features a premium touch screen digital control panel for the oven and the microwave offers convenient Sensor Cook and Auto Cook options.
